# MedTracker - Medication Reminder Web App

A responsive web application to help users track and manage their medications with browser notifications and Google Sheets backup.

![MedTracker Screenshot](screenshot.png)

## Features

- ðŸ’Š **Medication Management**
  - Add, edit and delete medications
  - Set medication schedules and frequencies
  - Mark medications as taken/untaken
  - View medication history

- ðŸ”” **Smart Notifications**
  - Browser notifications when it's time to take medications
  - Customizable reminder times
  - Works even when the browser is in background

- ðŸŒ“ **Modern UI/UX**
  - Clean, responsive design
  - Dark/light mode support
  - Mobile-first approach
  - Material Design inspired components

- ðŸ’¾ **Data Persistence**
  - Local storage for offline access
  - Google Sheets integration for backup
  - Real-time data synchronization
  - Multi-device support

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- A modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)
- A Google account (for Sheets integration)
- Basic knowledge of HTML/CSS/JavaScript

